==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Space walk
<hw>Space walk</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>any activity by a human outside
of the protective environment of a spacecraft while it is in outer
space, requiring a space suit to protect the person from the vacuum and
other hazards of space.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

